Author: jl777c#5810
Content: it is a peg maintain by having the supply adjusting, not a fixed supply peg

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: business cycles are nothing compared to crypto bull/bear cycles

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: as the crypto value goes up, it can support more stablecoins circulating, so this is allowed to happen

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: as the crypto value falls, the stablecoins are redeemed and the system balance restored

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: certainly if the crypto value goes to 0, it would cause a problem but as long as there is meaningful value in the crypto, it will support the stablecoins.
